{
  "text": "The efficacy of treatment was shown by the improvement of the IIEF scores during the sildenafil arm of the trial (Figure 2 ). The efficacy of sildenafil in treating ED in the general population exceeds 80%, [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] but this has never been studied in CHF. In our study, only 1 patient had no response at all to sildenafil (Figure 2) .",
